data.name: richTextBox1.Text
data.value:
This Auto-complete program helps you finish words as you type. Just write the first few letters, and the program will suggest full words that match what you're trying to say.
You can choose how the suggestions appear:
1-Most searched words first.
2-Shortest words first.
3-Alphabetical order.
You can also:
1-Add new words to the dictionary.
2-Delete words you don’t want.
3-if you search for a word 3 times and it’s not found, the program will remember it and save it automatically.
4-The program doesn't care about uppercase or lowercase – "Car" and "car" are treated the same. It also handles invalid or empty inputs smartly.
